behavioral_questions: Tell me about a time you had to work with a difficult teammate.
Tell me about a time you made a mistake at work. How did you handle it?
Tell me about a time you disagreed with a decision made by your manager.
Tell me about a time you had to learn something quickly to complete a task.
Tell me about a time you received critical feedback. How did you respond?
Tell me about a time you had to debug a difficult issue.
Tell me about a time when you had to balance multiple priorities.
Tell me about a time you worked on a team project. What role did you play?
Tell me about a time you failed to meet a deadline.
Tell me about a time when you had to deal with an unexpected challenge.
Tell me about a time you had to make a trade-off between code quality and speed.
Tell me about a time you had to communicate a complex technical concept to a non-technical audience.
Tell me about a time you had to refactor legacy code.
Tell me about a time you had to make a tough technical decision with limited data.
Tell me about a time you took initiative on a project.
Tell me about a time you mentored a teammate or junior engineer.
Tell me about a time when a project didn’t go as planned. What did you do?
Tell me about a time you contributed to improving team processes.
Tell me about a time you collaborated with cross-functional teams.
Tell me about a time you had to say no to a stakeholder.
Tell me about a time when your code caused a production issue.
Tell me about a time you improved system performance.
Tell me about a time you had to manage technical debt.
Tell me about a time you built something from scratch.
Tell me about a time you disagreed with an architectural decision.
Tell me about a time you had to handle an on-call incident.
Tell me about a time you had to prioritize between technical and business goals.
Tell me about a time you had to deal with scope creep.
Tell me about a time you challenged the status quo on your team.
Tell me about a time you exceeded expectations on a project.
Tell me about a time you missed something in a code review.
Tell me about a time you automated a repetitive task.
Tell me about a time you worked under tight deadlines.
Tell me about a time your team depended on you.
Tell me about a time you had to compromise on your solution.
Tell me about a time you made a significant impact on a project.
Tell me about a time you discovered a major issue late in the development cycle.
Tell me about a time you had to adapt to a new technology quickly.
Tell me about a time you got stuck on a problem and how you resolved it.
Tell me about a time you helped unblock someone else.
